
📌 Task

The DevOps team previously created a bare Git repository on the Storage Server. The application development team now requires a working copy of that repository for development.

Objective
Clone the existing Git repository located at /opt/blog.git
Clone it into /usr/src/kodekloudrepos
Perform the operation as the Natasha user
Do not modify repository permissions or existing directories
